reviews.text: Great hot pot place, Japanese style. Excellent variety of meats, veggies, toppings. It's unlimited for a fixed price so one can go nuts eating here. Great for groups. Service is fast and efficient

This is a nice place to go for lunch with friends for under 70. There is unlimited food, frozen yogurt and drinks. I have a had a few problems in the past with communication of the fact that one of my friends has religious requirements and thus needs her own hotpot, but that is a HK wide problem.
Love this place,  but there’s almost always a long que

Nice place for lunch hot pot buffet, nice environment, and reasonable price.
You can choose from different options on food, meat quality and time, but usually one hour is good enough for a lunch, and the vegetables and drinks are unlimited on all the options.  
And it's good that they refill the vegetables very fast, and with good enough options.  
Staffs will remind you when your dining time is about to end.  And the price is not expensive compare to other dining options in Causeway Bay.
You should expect your cloth become smelly after dining in here
Great quality beef and nice selection of buffet style vegetables to go with it. Soft serve frozen yogurt is a huge treat at the end! My current fav hot pot spot. Very affordable too!

reviews.text: This area of Hong Kong was recently redone. The shopping area is really cute with tons of stores. It is very clean the sales people are very helpful it's a few blocks away from times square mall. It's has lots of up  scale stores they are all very nice there is multiple buildings in the Lee Theater area so check the address to make sure you are in the correct building

Large shopping mall which is part of the Lee Gardens concept. Nice and functional, but not really with to much of a soul of is own or anything else to do really than to shop and eat. Functional rather than fantastic.

Your dinning place. Lots of nice restaurants in this building. 

Lower level are clothing shops. Upper levels are all restaurants. Take the lifts to go up to the higher levels.

this is a place to visit especially if you love shopping at UNIQLO. Several floors of UNIQLO assures you way better variety and stocks. Being located in causeway bay, it is convenient to explore from one shopping mall to another since the malls are just adjacent to each other.
The once iconic landmark theater turned shopping and dining center.
